title: Mike Pence Visits Georgia as Gov. Brian Kemp Plays Up Early Turnout
description: The former vice president was the first of several prominent Republicans who will visit before Election Day in support of Mr. Kemp.
dc:creator: Maya King
media:credit: Audra Melton for The New York Times
media:description: Former Vice President Mike Pence listed Gov. Brian Kemp’s conservative policy achievements on crime and abortion, and underscored Georgia’s role in national politics.
